00:23:49.039 --> 00:23:51.830
bring in the lost as quickly as I can

00:23:51.840 --> 00:23:54.390
because they're going to burn in hell.

00:23:54.400 --> 00:23:56.390
And what's most precious to him

00:23:56.400 --> 00:24:01.029
