the world, lay hands on the sick,

00:25:25.919 --> 00:25:28.950
cast out devils, raise the dead,

00:25:28.960 --> 00:25:30.950
to bring sight to the blind, to do

00:25:30.960 --> 00:25:33.190
everything the Lord told me I could do

00:25:33.200 --> 00:25:34.950
by His Word, and not get off in

00:25:34.950 --> 00:25:34.960
la-la

00:25:34.960 --> 00:25:36.470
land.

00:25:36.480 --> 00:25:38.950
Stay grounded in these last days, because

00:25:38.960 --> 00:25:40.549
you're going to get swayed by a lot of

