"Babe, does that witness with

00:25:53.590 --> 00:25:53.600
you?"Ah,

00:25:53.600 --> 00:25:55.269
don't listen to me. Okay.

00:25:55.279 --> 00:25:56.789
Well, let's pray some more until

00:25:56.799 --> 00:25:58.870
