little bit, but God, I'm still focused

00:26:16.000 --> 00:26:18.230
on

00:26:18.230 --> 00:26:18.240
You."Folks,

00:26:18.240 --> 00:26:20.310
when you miss it, you don't

00:26:20.320 --> 00:26:22.710
go, "Well, I'll quit."No, you just keep

